		<div class="navigation">
			<div class="alignleft">&laquo; <a href="http://ottopress.com/2012/themeplugin-dependencies/" rel="prev">Theme/Plugin Dependencies</a></div>
			<div class="alignright"><a href="http://ottopress.com/2012/how-to-leverage-the-theme-customizer-in-your-own-themes/" rel="next">How to leverage the Theme Customizer in your own themes</a> &raquo;</div>
