	<div itemprop="text"><p>I was curious how the combined form of the tacos and burritos would best be written taking _n() and argument swapping into account? As websites have become so dynamic in content and as most clients want message output to be spoken language, these situations seem to happen with increasing frequency. Thanks so much for the article. It is incredibly helpful.</p>
