	<li class="pingback even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-11839" itemprop="comment" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Comment">
		<div id="div-comment-11839" class="comment-body">
		<div class="comment-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
		<cite itemprop="name"><a itemprop='url' href='http://www.devin.com.br/php-gettext/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>php-gettext: Múltiplos idiomas em um sistema PHP - Devin</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>	</div>

